items.food_name: Hyderabadi Dum Biryani - Slow-cooked rice with aromatic spices and tender meat

biryani.name: Royal Awadhi Biryani
biryani.description: A fragrant and flavorful biryani cooked with premium basmati rice, succulent mutton pieces, and a blend of secret Awadhi spices. Slow-cooked in a sealed handi for the perfect taste.

biryani.name: Zam Zam Special Chicken Biryani
biryani.description: A Kolkata-style chicken biryani with juicy chicken pieces, aromatic saffron-infused rice, and the signature potato that makes it unique to the city. Served with raita.

biryani.name: Aminia Mutton Biryani
biryani.description: A legendary dish from one of Kolkata's oldest biryani houses. Tender mutton pieces, flavorful rice, and a perfectly balanced spice mix, topped with a soft-boiled potato and caramelized onions.

biryani.name: Shiraz Chicken Biryani
biryani.description: A true delight for chicken lovers! This Kolkata-style biryani features marinated chicken, fragrant rice, and the city's signature potato, cooked to perfection.

biryani.name: Oudh 1590 Raan Biryani
biryani.description: A luxurious biryani experience with a slow-cooked whole lamb leg, infused with rich Awadhi flavors. A royal treat for those who love authentic biryani.

biryani.name: Arsalan Special Chicken Biryani
biryani.description: A Kolkata favorite! Fragrant basmati rice, juicy chicken, and a soft potato, all slow-cooked with authentic Mughlai spices. Served with raita and salad.

biryani.name: Rehmania Beef Biryani
biryani.description: A hidden gem in the streets of Kolkata, this beef biryani is slow-cooked to perfection with rich spices and tender beef pieces, making it an absolute delight.

biryani.name: Haji Saheb Dum Biryani
biryani.description: This biryani is prepared in a traditional dum-style, with aromatic rice, tender meat, and rich masala, creating an unforgettable taste experience.

biryani.name: Kolkata Egg Biryani
biryani.description: For egg lovers, this biryani is a must-try! Spiced rice, boiled eggs, and the signature potato, making it a delicious and affordable meal.

biryani.name: Kolkata Veg Biryani
biryani.description: A vegetarian twist on Kolkata's iconic biryani, featuring aromatic rice, flavorful paneer, and the signature potato, cooked with fragrant spices.

rolls.name: Kolkata Egg Roll
rolls.description: A crispy paratha wrap filled with a flavorful egg omelet, onions, and tangy sauces, a street food classic of Kolkata.

rolls.name: Chicken Kathi Roll
rolls.description: Juicy and spicy chicken pieces wrapped in a soft paratha, topped with onions, chutneys, and a dash of lemon.

rolls.name: Mutton Seekh Kebab Roll
rolls.description: Succulent mutton seekh kebabs rolled in a buttery paratha, complemented by fresh salad and mint chutney.

rolls.name: Double Egg Chicken Roll
rolls.description: A double dose of eggs with spiced chicken pieces wrapped in a crispy paratha, a filling delight for food lovers.

rolls.name: Paneer Tikka Roll
rolls.description: Soft paneer cubes marinated in tikka spices, grilled to perfection, and wrapped in a warm paratha with onions and chutney.

rolls.name: Cheese Chicken Roll
rolls.description: A fusion delight featuring cheesy chicken chunks with a hint of spice, wrapped in a crispy paratha.

rolls.name: Fish Tandoori Roll
rolls.description: A Kolkata special featuring tender fish tandoori chunks rolled in a soft paratha with fresh salad and mint chutney.

rolls.name: Mix Veg Roll
rolls.description: A delicious combination of saut√©ed vegetables and spices wrapped in a paratha, perfect for vegetarians.

rolls.name: Spicy Chicken Bhuna Roll
rolls.description: Slow-cooked chicken bhuna, rich in spices and flavors, wrapped in a buttery paratha for an ultimate taste experience.

rolls.name: Malai Tikka Roll
rolls.description: A creamy and mildly spiced chicken malai tikka roll, offering a melt-in-the-mouth experience with every bite.

salads.name: Kolkata Special Chicken Salad
salads.description: A refreshing salad with grilled chicken, fresh greens, cucumbers, tomatoes, and a tangy mustard dressing inspired by Kolkata flavors.

salads.name: Egg and Veggie Salad
salads.description: A protein-packed salad featuring boiled eggs, crunchy vegetables, and a light lemon dressing, perfect for a healthy meal.

salads.name: Paneer Tikka Salad
salads.description: Tandoori paneer cubes tossed with fresh lettuce, onions, and a spicy yogurt dressing for a flavorful experience.

salads.name: Mutton Kebab Salad
salads.description: Juicy mutton kebabs sliced and served over a bed of greens, complemented with a spicy mint dressing.

salads.name: Spicy Masala Corn Salad
salads.description: A street-style corn salad mixed with tangy spices, onions, and fresh coriander for a burst of flavors.

salads.name: Fish Tandoori Salad
salads.description: Grilled fish tandoori fillets served with crunchy vegetables and a zesty lime dressing for a refreshing meal.

salads.name: Classic Green Salad
salads.description: A simple yet fresh mix of lettuce, cucumbers, tomatoes, and onions, drizzled with olive oil and herbs.

salads.name: Kolkata Chaat Salad
salads.description: A fusion of Kolkata street food flavors, featuring crispy sev, potatoes, chickpeas, and tangy tamarind dressing.

salads.name: Sprout and Moong Dal Salad
salads.description: A nutritious and protein-rich salad with sprouted moong dal, chopped vegetables, and a hint of lemon.

salads.name: Beetroot and Yogurt Salad
salads.description: A cooling beetroot and yogurt salad with a mild spice kick, perfect for a refreshing side dish.

muglai.name: Mughlai Chicken Korma
muglai.description: A rich and creamy Mughlai-style chicken korma, slow-cooked with aromatic spices, cashew paste, and yogurt for a royal taste.

muglai.name: Mutton Rogan Josh
muglai.description: Tender mutton pieces cooked in a flavorful, mildly spicy tomato-based gravy with a hint of saffron and Kashmiri red chilies.

muglai.name: Shahi Paneer
muglai.description: Soft paneer cubes simmered in a rich, creamy, and mildly spiced tomato-cashew gravy, fit for royalty.

muglai.name: Murgh Musallam
muglai.description: A whole chicken marinated in exotic Mughlai spices, slow-cooked in a flavorful, nutty, and creamy gravy for a regal experience.

muglai.name: Mughlai Paratha
muglai.description: A delicious, crispy, and stuffed paratha filled with minced meat, eggs, and spices, served with tangy chutney.

muglai.name: Nawabi Pulao
muglai.description: A fragrant Mughlai-style rice dish made with long-grain Basmati rice, saffron, dry fruits, and mild spices.

muglai.name: Chicken Reshmi Kebab
muglai.description: Soft and juicy chicken kebabs made with cream, cashew paste, and mild spices, grilled to perfection.

muglai.name: Mutton Galouti Kebab
muglai.description: Melt-in-the-mouth mutton kebabs made with a rich blend of Mughlai spices, best enjoyed with paratha or naan.

muglai.name: Badami Gosht
muglai.description: A royal Mughlai delicacy featuring tender mutton cooked in a luscious almond-based gravy with exotic spices.

muglai.name: Malai Kofta
muglai.description: Soft, creamy koftas made from paneer and potatoes, served in a rich, velvety Mughlai-style gravy.

items.food_name: Chicken Biryani - Juicy chicken pieces layered with fragrant basmati rice

biryani.name: Royal Awadhi Biryani
biryani.description: A regal blend of fragrant basmati rice, tender mutton, and a secret mix of spices, cooked in traditional dum style for an authentic Awadhi taste.

biryani.name: Kolkata Special Chicken Biryani
biryani.description: A signature dish of Kolkata, this biryani features aromatic rice, succulent chicken, and a perfectly cooked potato, infused with delicate Mughlai flavors.

biryani.name: Mughlai Mutton Biryani
biryani.description: Rich and flavorful, this mutton biryani is slow-cooked with saffron-infused rice, juicy mutton pieces, and an exquisite blend of royal spices.

biryani.name: Handi Chicken Biryani
biryani.description: Prepared in an earthen pot, this biryani offers a rustic taste with juicy chicken, fragrant rice, and a smoky aroma that lingers delightfully.

biryani.name: Nizam's Special Beef Biryani
biryani.description: A rich, flavorful biryani made with tender beef pieces, slow-cooked to perfection with aromatic rice and a symphony of traditional spices.

biryani.name: Bengali Prawn Biryani
biryani.description: A seafood delight, this prawn biryani blends the sweetness of fresh prawns with the bold spices of Kolkata's biryani tradition.

biryani.name: Hyderabadi Biryani (Kolkata Style)
biryani.description: A fusion of Hyderabadi and Kolkata biryani styles, featuring flavorful rice, juicy mutton, and a unique spice blend for an unforgettable taste.

biryani.name: Reshmi Chicken Biryani
biryani.description: Creamy, succulent chicken pieces cooked with saffron-infused rice, topped with caramelized onions and a hint of rose water for a royal touch.

biryani.name: Egg Biryani
biryani.description: A budget-friendly yet flavorful biryani, featuring perfectly spiced eggs, fragrant rice, and a balanced mix of traditional Kolkata spices.

biryani.name: Vegetable Dum Biryani
biryani.description: A delightful vegetarian option, cooked with seasonal vegetables, aromatic rice, and a carefully curated blend of traditional spices.
